Usage

* Plugin configuration

	You should specify the version in your project's plugin configuration:

+---------------------
<project>
  ...
  <build>
    <!-- To use the plugin goals, add the following in your POM or parent POM -->
    <plugins>
      <plugin>
        <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
        <artifactId>${project.artifactId}</artifactId>
        <version>${project.version}</version>
        <configuration>
          <!--
          <packageName>my-package</packageName>
          <packageVersion>1.0.0</packageVersion>
          ...
          -->
        </configuration>
      </plugin>
      ...
    </plugins>
  </build>
  ...
</project>
+---------------------

	You probably also need to specify the location of the debian-maven-plugin repository:

+---------------------
<project>
  ...
  <pluginRepositories>
    <pluginRepository>
      <id>debian-maven.sourceforge.net</id>
      <url>http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/debian-maven/m2repo</url>
      <snapshots><enabled>false</enabled></snapshots>
    </pluginRepository>
  </pluginRepositories>
  ...
</project>
+---------------------

